@non1337 : They actually errataed it once before to make it non-broken (for a while, it used Time counters, so untapping it couldn't cheat it.)  

They decided to switch it back because nowadays errata are only supposed to make a card work as it originally worked, not to change its functionality.  

(Hmm, even when it first came out, long before Voltaic Key, you could break it with [Animate Artifact](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Animate Artifact) and [Instill Energy](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Instill Energy). That was a more complex combo and opened it to creature removal, though, so it was probably considered acceptable.)

